imdb.plot outline: Entrepreneurs are shaping the future across the globe with their radical visions for innovative solutions to big problems. From San Francisco to Lagos to Dubai and more, this series probes their brilliant minds and souls through a Proust Questionnaire-inspired session to reveal their deepest inspirations and challenges - helping the rest of us discover what it's really like to be an entrepreneur. In these interviews, founders reveal the realities of building a startup, both the difficulties, which often unspoken, and the rewards of meeting the challenges of establishing a new business. Viewers are inspired and educated by sharing the reality and passion of the entrepreneurial journey.
